@DATABASE "Savage Part 3"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - S - Savage Part 3"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - S
                   ====================================

                               Savage Part 3
                               =============



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(34398,99)"}         34398,99
@{"Infinite Lives " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(57848,183)"}         57848,183
@{"Infinite Energy" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(57919,0)"}         57919,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
